-- AIG in Talks to Sell India Asset Management Unit, Mint Reports
-- B y   A n i l   V a r m a
-- 2010-10-04T02:04:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-04/aig-in-talks-to-sell-india-asset-management-unit-mint-reports.html
American International Group Inc. is
planning to sell its asset management unit in India and has
hired Bank of America-Merrill Lynch to arrange the sale, the
Mint reported, without saying where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
